extracted_rules.rule: Height measurement on land with natural slope ≤ 10%

Qualifiers.Applicability: Structures on land with natural slope ≤ 10%

extracted_rules.rule: Height measurement on land with natural slope > 10%

Qualifiers.Applicability: Structures on land with natural slope > 10%

Constants.Procedures: Use the lower of existing or finished grade

Conditions.Mandatory: The structure must comply with the lower of the two limits at all points along the slope
